			<tr><td colspan="2">
				<div class="postbody">
				The exploration and exploitation of space has the potential to cure a lot of basic problems. Can cut down on pollution by ending most terrestrial mining, for example.
<br />

<br />
Been too long since we've been to the moon, we've been due back there for quite some time. The technologies they have developed and will develop for space exploration oftentimes have tremendous benefit for the average citizen. 
<br />

<br />
I'm mostly worried about 2 things:
<br />
1) How the hell we are going to pay for it.
<br />
2) Whether or not this is just a re-election stunt.<br />
				<span class="gensmall"></span><br />
